                "isi_post" => "<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Berdasarkan hasil keputusan Departemen Pusat Komputer Pemenang Lomba Blog Politeknik Caltex Riau yang telah berjalan selama 6 bulan. Maka diambillah 3 orang peserta teratas yang menempati leaderboard, Berikut adalah daftar peserta yang memenangkan lomba ini<\/span><\/p>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"page-break-after: always\"><span style=\"display:none\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/div>\r\n\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"width:581px\">\r\n\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td style=\"height:21px; text-align:center; width:33px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\">&nbsp;J<span style=\"font-size:12px\">UARA&nbsp;<\/span><\/span><\/td>\r\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center; width:167px\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">NAMA<\/span><\/td>\r\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center; width:101px\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">PRODI<\/span><\/td>\r\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center; width:121px\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">ANGKATAN<\/span><\/td>\r\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center; width:159px\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">BLOG<\/span><\/td>\r\n\t\t<\/tr>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td style=\"height:21px; text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">1<\/span><\/td>\r\n\t\t\t<td><span style=\"font-size:12px\">Rengki Fauzan<\/span><\/td>\r\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">TI<\/span><\/td>\r\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">2015<\/span><\/td>\r\n\t\t\t<td><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><a href=\"http:\/\/fauzan.blog.pcr.ac.id\/\">fauzan.blog.pcr.ac.id<\/a><\/span><\/td>\r\n\t\t<\/tr>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td style=\"height:21px; text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">2<\/span><\/td>\r\n\t\t\t<td><span style=\"font-size:12px\">Dhimas Sena Rahmantara<\/span><\/td>\r\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">TI<\/span><\/td>\r\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-