                "status_post" => "published",
                "meta_desc_post" => "Pusat Unggulan Teknologi (PUT) Politeknik Caltex Riau (PCR) telah mengadakan Training Operator dan Programming Computer Numerical Control (CNC) pada tanggal 21 ",
