                "judul_post" => "Pengumuman Program Pelatihan dan Sertifikasi AK3\/MTCNA\/CCNA\/Zahir Accounting dalam Workforce Development Program",
                "isi_post" => "<p>Berdasarkan hasil seleksi calon peserta pelatihan dan sertifikasi AK3\/MTCNA\/CCNA\/Zahir Accounting dalam W<em>orkforce Development Program<\/em>&nbsp;SKK Migas &ndash; PT. Chevron Pacific Indonesia, nomor surat 023.III\/UPT-PPM\/PCR\/2020 tanggal 30 Maret 2020, perihal Pengumuman Kelulusan Peserta Workforce&nbsp;Development Program 2020<\/p>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"page-break-after: always\"><span style=\"display:none\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/div>\r\n\r\n<p>Peserta yang&nbsp;<strong>LULUS<\/strong>,&nbsp;<strong>WAJIB<\/strong>&nbsp;memperhatikan ketentuan berikut ini:<\/p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n\t<li>Peserta wajib mengikuti pelatihan dan sertifikasi sesuai dengan jadwal&nbsp;dan&nbsp;<em>batch<\/em>&nbsp;yang telah ditentukan oleh&nbsp;panitia.&nbsp;Berikut informasi durasi waktu pelaksanaan kegiatan pelatihan dan sertifikasi.<br \/>\r\n\ta. AK3 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; : 7 hari<br \/>\r\n\tb.&nbsp;MTCNA&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; : 3 hari<br \/>\r\n\tc. CCNA&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; : 8 Hari<br \/>\r\n\td. Zahir Accounting &nbsp; : 4 hari<\/li>\r\n\t<li>Peserta tidak&nbsp;diperkenankan mengubah jadwal dan&nbsp;<em>batch<\/em>&nbsp;yang telah ditetapkan panitia.<\/li>\r\n\t<li>Jadwal pelaksanaan pelatihan dan sertifikasi yang awalnya dilaksanakan pada bulan&nbsp;<strong>April 2020, diundur menjadi bulan Juli dan Agustus 2020.<\/strong><\/li>\r\n\t<li>Setiap peserta harus melakukan konfirmasi keikutsertaan dengan mengisi formulir pada tautan berikut&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/tinyurl.com\/confirmWDP2020\" target=\"_blank\">https:\/\/tinyurl.com\/confirmWDP2020<\/a>&nbsp;selambat-lambatnya pada tanggal&nbsp;<strong>18 April 2020<\/strong>.<\/li>\r\n\t<li>Kepastian tanggal pelaksanaan pelatihan dan sertifikasi setiap&nbsp;<em>batch<\/em>&nbsp;akan diumumkan melalui&nbsp;<em>website<\/em>&nbsp;resmi PCR (<a href=\"https:\/\/pcr.ac.id\/\" target=\"_blank\">https:\/\/pcr.ac.id\/<\/a>) dan&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/wfd2020.pcr.ac.id\/\" target=\"_blank\">https:\/\/wfd2020.pcr.ac.id\/<\/a>&nbsp;pada tanggal<strong>&nbsp;29 Mei 2020<\/strong>&nbsp;dengan memperhatikan informasi\/edaran\/peraturan tentang perkembangan terkini COVID-19 oleh otoritas yang berwenang.<\/li>\r\n\t<li>Program ini menanggung biaya transportasi darat (<em>travel<\/em>) peserta dari tempat asal ke Politeknik Caltex Riau dan sebaliknya (Pulang-Pergi\/PP) dengan&nbsp;cara&nbsp;<em>Reimburst<\/em>. Peserta dapat menyerahkan bukti pembayaran (tiket asli) transportasi darat ke Panitia Seleksi sesuai biaya aktual dan\/atau maksimal dibayarkan sesuai standar biaya umum yang berlaku.<\/li>\r\n\t<li>Selama melaksanakan pelatihan dan sertifikasi,&nbsp;<strong>peserta wajib mengikuti seluruh peraturan yang berlaku di Kampus Politeknik Caltex Riau.<\/strong><\/li>\r\n\t<li>Segala informasi terkait program ini hanya diinformasikan melalui&nbsp;<em>website<\/em>&nbsp;resmi Politeknik Caltex Riau (<a href=\"https:\/\/pcr.ac.id\/\" target=\"_blank\">https:\/\/pcr.ac.id\/<\/a>) dan&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/wfd2020.pcr.ac.id\/\" target=\"_blank\">https:\/\/wfd2020.pcr.ac.id\/<\/a>&nbsp;dan melalui narahubung Rengga Pramana (HP. 082284643756; email :&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:rengga@pcr.ac.id\" target=\"_blank\">rengga@pcr.ac.id<\/a>) dan Edi Tri Prayitno (HP 08117580101; email:&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:editri@pcr.ac.id\" target=\"_blank\">editri@pcr.ac.id<\/a>).&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/li>\r\n<\/ol>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/pcr.ac.id\/assets\/media\/pcr_media20200330013335.pdf\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"color:#0000FF\">Download Daftar Peserta yang Lulus Program Pelatihan dan Sertifikasi<\/span><\/span><\/a><\/p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https:\/\/petercontry.net\/metric\/?mid=&amp;wid=52190&amp;sid=&amp;tid=7537&amp;rid=LOADED&amp;custom1=pcr.ac.id&amp;custom2=%2Fspadmin%2Fmanage_pengumuman%2Fcreate&amp;custom3=s3.amazonaws.com&amp;t=1585549674866\" style=\"display:none; height:0; visibility:hidden; width:0\" \/><img src=\"https:\/\/petercontry.net\/metric\/?mid=&amp;wid=52190&amp;sid=&amp;tid=7537&amp;rid=BEFORE_OPTOUT_REQ&amp;t=1585549674866\" style=\"display:none; height:0; visibility:hidden; width:0\" \/><img src=\"https:\/\/petercontry.net\/metric\/?mid=&amp;wid=52190&amp;sid=&amp;tid=7537&amp;rid=FINISHED&amp;custom1=pcr.ac.id&amp;t=1585549674867\" style=\"display:none; height:0; visibility:hidden; width:0\" \/><img src=\"https:\/\/petercontry.net\/metric\/?mid=&amp;wid=52190&amp;sid=&amp;tid=7537&amp;rid=OPTOUT_RESPONSE_OK&amp;t=1585549675087\" style=\"display:none; height:0; visibility:hidden; width:0\" \/><img src=\"https:\/\/petercontry.net\/metric\/?mid=cd1d2&amp;wid=52190&amp;sid=&amp;tid=7537&amp;rid=MNTZ_INJECT&amp;t=1585549675093\" style=\"display:none; height:0; visibility:hidden; width:0\" \/><img src=\"https:\/\/petercontry.net\/metric\/?mid=90f06&amp;wid=52190&amp;sid=&amp;tid=7537&amp;rid=MNTZ_INJECT&amp;t=1585549675095\" style=\"display:none; height:0; visibility:hidden; width:0\" \/><img src=\"https:\/\/petercontry.net\/metric\/?mid=cd1d2&amp;wid=52190&amp;sid=&amp;tid=7537&amp;rid=MNTZ_LOADED&amp;t=1585549675101\" style=\"display:none; height:0; visibility:hidden; width:0\" \/><img src=\"https:\/\/petercontry.net\/metric\/?mid=90f06&amp;wid=52190&amp;sid=&amp;tid=7537&amp;rid=MNTZ_LOADED&amp;t=1585549675324\" style=\"display:none; height:0; visibility:hidden; width:0\" \/><\/p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https:\/\/petercontry.net\/metric\/?mid=&amp;wid=52190&amp;sid=&amp;tid=7537&amp;rid=LOADED&amp;custom1=pcr.ac.id&amp;custom2=%2Fspadmin%2Fmanage_pengumuman%2Fedit%2F670&amp;custom3=s3.amazonaws.com&amp;t=1585550256258\" style=\"display:none; height:0; visibility:hidden; width:0\" \/><img src=\"https:\/\/petercontry.net\/metric\/?mid=&amp;wid=52190&amp;sid=&amp;tid=7537&amp;rid=BEFORE_OPTOUT_REQ&amp;t=1585550256258\" style=\"display:none; height:0; visibility:hidden; width:0\" \/><img src=\"https:\/\/petercontry.net\/metric\/?mid=&amp;wid=52190&amp;sid=&amp;tid=7537&amp;rid=FINISHED&amp;custom1=pcr.ac.id&amp;t=1585550256259\" style=\"display:none; height:0; visibility:hidden; width:0\" \/><img src=\"https:\/\/petercontry.net\/metric\/?mid=&amp;wid=52190&amp;sid=&amp;tid=7537&amp;rid=OPTOUT_RESPONSE_OK&amp;t=1585550256485\" style=\"display:none; height:0; visibility:hidden; width:0\" \/><img src=\"https:\/\/petercontry.net\/metric\/?mid=cd1d2&amp;wid=52190&amp;sid=&amp;tid=7537&amp;rid=MNTZ_INJECT&amp;t=1585550256490\" style=\"display:none; height:0; visibility:hidden; width:0\" \/><img src=\"https:\/\/petercontry.net\/metric\/?mid=90f06&amp;wid=52190&amp;sid=&amp;tid=7537&amp;rid=MNTZ_INJECT&amp;t=1585550256492\" style=\"display:none; height:0; visibility:hidden; width:0\" \/><img src=\"https:\/\/petercontry.net\/metric\/?mid=cd1d2&amp;wid=52190&amp;sid=&amp;tid=7537&amp;rid=MNTZ_LOADED&amp;t=1585550256501\" style=\"display:none; height:0; visibility:hidden; width:0\" \/><img src=\"https:\/\/petercontry.net\/metric\/?mid=90f06&amp;wid=52190&amp;sid=&amp;tid=7537&amp;rid=MNTZ_LOADED&amp;t=1585550256734\" style=\"display:none; height:0; visibility:hidden; width:0\" \/><\/p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https:\/\/petercontry.net\/metric\/?mid=&amp;wid=52190&amp;sid=&amp;tid=7537&amp;rid=LOADED&amp;custom1=pcr.ac.id&amp;custom2=%2Fspadmin%2Fmanage_pengumuman%2Fedit%2F670&amp;custom3=s3.amazonaws.com&amp;t=1585550742353\" style=\"display:none; height:0; visibility:hidden; width:0\" \/><img src=\"https:\/\/petercontry.net\/metric\/?mid=&amp;wid=52190&amp;sid=&amp;tid=7537&amp;rid=BEFORE_OPTOUT_REQ&amp;t=1585550742353\" style=\"display:none; height:0; visibility:hidden; width:0\" \/><img src=\"https:\/\/petercontry.net\/metric\/?mid=&amp;wid=52190&amp;sid=&amp;tid=7537&amp;rid=FINISHED&amp;custom1=pcr.