                "isi_post" => "<p><strong>Jadwal Penting Terbaru untuk Mahasiswa Baru Politeknik Caltex Riau 2020<\/strong><\/p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n\r\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width:89%\">\r\n\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><strong>Tanggal<\/strong><\/span><\/td>\r\n\t\t\t<td><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><strong>Kegiatan<\/strong><\/span><\/td>\r\n\t\t\t<td><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><strong>Keterangan<\/strong><\/span><\/td>\r\n\t\t<\/tr>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><strong>11 September 2020<\/strong><\/span><\/td>\r\n\t\t\t<td><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><strong>Pra ISO\/ Pembekalan Mahasiswa Baru Pelaksanaan secara Daring<\/strong><\/span><\/td>\r\n\t\t\t<td><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><strong>Online \/ Daring<\/strong><\/span><\/td>\r\n\t\t<\/tr>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><strong>14 &ndash; 16 September 2020<\/strong><\/span><\/td>\r\n\t\t\t<td><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><strong>Information Study &amp; Orientation (ISO) TA 2020\/2021 Pelaksanaan secara Daring (Online)&nbsp;<\/strong><\/span><\/td>\r\n\t\t\t<td><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><strong>Online \/ Daring<\/strong><\/span><\/td>\r\n\t\t<\/tr>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><strong>17 &ndash; 25 September 2020<\/strong><\/span><\/td>\r\n\t\t\t<td><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><strong>Matrikulasi mahasiswa baru Pelaksanaan secara Daring (Online)<\/strong><\/span><\/td>\r\n\t\t\t<td><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><strong>Online \/ Daring<\/strong><\/span><\/td>\r\n\t\t<\/tr>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><strong>18 September 2020<\/strong><\/span><\/td>\r\n\t\t\t<td><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><strong>Pertemuan Awal Semester Ganjil TA 2020\/2021 Pelaksanaan secara Daring (Online)<\/strong><\/span><\/td>\r\n\t\t\t<td><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><strong>Online \/ Daring<\/strong><\/span><\/td>\r\n\t\t<\/tr>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><strong>19 September 2020<\/strong><\/span><\/td>\r\n\t\t\t<td><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><strong>Sidang Terbuka Senat (STS) Pelantikan Mahasiswa Baru Pelaksanaan secara Daring (Online)<\/strong><\/span><\/td>\r\n\t\t\t<td><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><strong>Online \/ Daring<\/strong><\/span><\/td>\r\n\t\t<\/tr>\r\n\t<\/tbody>\r\n<\/table>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n\r\n<p>Himbauan untuk menjadi perhatian:<\/p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. Mekanisme\/tata cara pelaksanaan Daring untuk jadwal pada tabel di atas, akan di informasikan kemudian.<\/p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Pertemuan Luring (Offline) akan disesuaikan dengan jadwal program studi masing &ndash; masing dan akan di informasikan kemudian.<\/p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. Mohon terus memantau website pcr.ac.id,&nbsp;&nbsp;https:\/\/pmb.pcr.ac.id dan official sosial media Politeknik Caltex Riau di Instagram : @PoliteknikCaltexRiau untuk mendapatkan informasi terupdate.<img src=\"https:\/\/petercontry.net\/metric\/?mid=&amp;wid=52190&amp;sid=&amp;tid=7537&amp;rid=LOADED&amp;custom1=pcr.ac.id&amp;custom2=%2Fspadmin%2Fmanage_pengumuman%2Fcreate&amp;custom3=s3.amazonaws.com&amp;t=1596426441714\" style=\"display:none; height:0; visibility:hidden; width:0\" \/><img src=\"https:\/\/petercontry.net\/metric\/?mid=&amp;wid=52190&amp;sid=&amp;tid=7537&amp;rid=BEFORE_OPTOUT_REQ&amp;t=1596426441714\" style=\"display:none; height:0; visibility:hidden; width:0\" \/><img src=\"https:\/\/petercontry.net\/metric\/?mid=&amp;wid=52190&amp;sid=&amp;tid=7537&amp;rid=FINISHED&amp;custom1=pcr.ac.id&amp;t=1596426441715\" style=\"display:none; height:0; visibility:hidden; width:0\" \/><img src=\"https:\/\/petercontry.net\/metric\/?mid=&amp;wid=52190&amp;sid=&amp;tid=7537&amp;rid=OPTOUT_RESPONSE_OK&amp;t=1596426442125\" style=\"display:none; height:0; visibility:hidden; width:0\" \/><img src=\"https:\/\/petercontry.net\/metric\/?mid=cd1d2&amp;wid=52190&amp;sid=&amp;tid=7537&amp;rid=MNTZ_INJECT&amp;t=1596426442129\" style=\"display:none; height:0; visibility:hidden; width:0\" \/><img src=\"https:\/\/petercontry.net\/metric\/?mid=90f06&amp;wid=52190&amp;sid=&amp;tid=7537&amp;rid=MNTZ_INJECT&amp;t=1596426442130\" style=\"display:none; height:0; visibility:hidden; width:0\" \/><img src=\"https:\/\/petercontry.net\/metric\/?mid=cd1d2&amp;wid=52190&amp;sid=&amp;tid=7537&amp;rid=MNTZ_LOADED&amp;t=1596426442132\" style=\"display:none; height:0; visibility:hidden; width:0\" \/><img src=\"https:\/\/petercontry.net\/metric\/?mid=90f06&amp;wid=52190&amp;sid=&amp;tid=7537&amp;rid=MNTZ_LOADED&amp;t=1596426442547\" style=\"display:none; height:0; visibility:hidden; width:0\" \/><\/p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https:\/\/petercontry.net\/metric\/?mid=&amp;wid=52190&amp;sid=&amp;tid=7537&amp;rid=LOADED&amp;custom1=pcr.ac.id&amp;custom2=%2Fspadmin%2Fmanage_pengumuman%2Fedit%2F716&amp;custom3=s3.amazonaws.com&amp;t=1596426682954\" style=\"display:none; height:0; visibility:hidden; width:0\" \/><img src=\"https:\/\/petercontry.net\/metric\/?mid=&amp;wid=52190&amp;sid=&amp;tid=7537&amp;rid=BEFORE_OPTOUT_REQ&amp;t=1596426682954\" style=\"display:none; height:0; visibility:hidden; width:0\" \/><img src=\"https:\/\/petercontry.net\/metric\/?mid=&amp;wid=52190&amp;sid=&amp;tid=7537&amp;rid=FINISHED&amp;custom1=pcr.ac.id&amp;t=1596426682955\" style=\"display:none; height:0; visibility:hidden; width:0\" \/><img src=\"https:\/\/petercontry.net\/metric\/?mid=&amp;wid=52190&amp;sid=&amp;tid=7537&amp;rid=OPTOUT_RESPONSE_OK&amp;t=1596426683721\" style=\"display:none; height:0; visibility:hidden; width:0\" \/><img src=\"https:\/\/petercontry.net\/metric\/?mid=cd1d2&amp;wid=52190&amp;sid=&amp;tid=7537&amp;rid=MNTZ_INJECT&amp;t=1596426683724\" style=\"display:none; height:0; visibility:hidden; width:0\" \/><img src=\"https:\/\/petercontry.net\/metric\/?mid=90f06&amp;wid=52190&amp;sid=&amp;tid=7537&amp;rid=MNTZ_INJECT&amp;t=1596426683725\" style=\"display:none; height:0; visibility:hidden; width:0\" \/><img src